Author: red_ossifrage
Text: Legitimately, if I weren't such an impatient person I doubt I would have anorexia. I'd still have EDNOS or something, but my inability to focus on long term goals (thanks, ADHD) was for sure one of my risk factors for extreme restrictive eating.   I'm sorry you're going through this pain, and hope things improve soon!
